{"tid":1933514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(美國國會) 兩黨議員確診","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T18:04:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":135,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"6a38141ddc2017867fc8dd810d119eef2201f9d4","tid":1933514,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2594783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2594783&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=1b65f634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2594783</a><br />\n<br />\n美國疫情】國會也失守 2眾議員確診<br />\n環球政治 12:59 2020/03/19 <br />\n<br />\n美國的新冠肺炎疫情蔓延，全美國50個州份相繼失守，美國國會也難逃疫情侵襲。美國眾議院2名眾議員同日先後確診新冠肺炎，包括眾議院佛羅里達州共和黨眾議員迪亞茲-巴拉特（Mario Diaz-Balart），及猶他州的民主黨眾議員麥克亞當斯（Ben McAdams）。"},{"pid":"7abbe6225c1708592d2be1b487871ce24aeed095","tid":1933514,"uid":134071,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"大家要去確診議員既twitter打氣, 展現香港人的友善<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/RepBenMcAdams\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepBenMcAdams&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=1b0f57e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/RepBenMcAdams</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/mariodb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmariodb&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=fc3f8240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/mariodb</a>"},{"pid":"a834524b7eb079a93a7d579b3c2c4f506a0da22a","tid":1933514,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e7c02ae02aeb7e7ffeadbc83a0e8f4aea0790b","tid":1933514,"uid":265839,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:30:03.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/asset